    <facet>

    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1770207016</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">Vieux Carr?: A Creole Neighborhood in New Orleans</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Vieux Carr?: Eine kreolische Nachbarschaft 
in New-Orleans</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Vieux Carr ? : Un voisinage créole à la 
Nouvelle-Orléans</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Vieux Carr?: Uma vizinhança creole em Nova 
Orleães</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Vieux Carr?: Una vicinanza creola a New 
Orleans</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Vieux Carr;: Μια κρεολική γειτονιά στη Νέα
Ορλεάνη</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Vieux Carr?: Una vecindad criolla en New 
Orleans</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">looks at the history of the French Quarter, the heart and soul of modern New Orleans and a constant reminder of the city's Creole, colonial past.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Blicke auf die Geschichte des französischen 
Viertels, des Inneren und der Seele von modernem New-Orleans und der 
konstanten Anzeige des Kreolen der Stadt, Kolonialvergangenheit.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">regards à l'histoire du quartier français, du 
coeur et de l'âme de la Nouvelle-Orléans moderne et d'un rappel 
constant du Créole de la ville, passé colonial.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">olhares no history do quarto francês, do 
coração e da alma de Nova Orleães moderna e de um lembrete 
constante do creole da cidade, passado colonial.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">sguardi alla storia del quarto francese, del cuore
e dell'anima di New Orleans moderna e di un ricordo costante del 
creolo della città, esperienza coloniale.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">εξετάζει την ιστορία του γαλλικού τετάρτου, της 
καρδιάς και της ψυχής της σύγχρονης Νέας Ορλεάνης και μιας 
σταθερής υπενθύμισης του κρεολικού, αποικιακού παρελθόντος της 
πόλης.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">miradas en la historia del cuarto francés, del 
corazón y del alma de New Orleans moderna y de un recordatorio 
constante del criollo de la ciudad, pasado colonial.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciências Sociais</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Scienze Sociali</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Κοινωνικές επιστήμες</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ciencias Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
